Title: ZK Social Club @ SBC
Description:
Succinct is hosting the inaugural ZK Social Club at SBC to allow builders and researchers interested in ZK technology and its applications to learn, socialize and build together.

ZK Social Club brings together technical workshops, community talks, hacker house energy and co-working space, in the spirit of advancing the broader ZK ecosystem.

Learn more at: http://zksocial.club/

Schedule

Each day of the week will have a special focus. During the day, there will be talks and workshops about the given theme, and time set aside for participants to get their hands dirty and build with technical guidance and mentorship. In the evenings, there will be a keynote talk from a speaker in the community. The full agenda for each day and list of speakers will be announced soon!
Monday: Going 0 -> 1 on ZK and integrating it into your DApp 
Tuesday: Plonky2 Day 
Wednesday: ZK Light Clients
Thursday: ZK Hackathon (win $5k in prizes!)
